Typical drones are "one trick ponies," only able to either fly or film and nothing else.  With our waterproof drone and family of quick change pods accessories, the AguaDrone is the workhorse of drones! The AguaDrone is capable of doing more, going where no other drone can go, and adapting to the end-users needs better than any drone on the market. Find Pod: Sonar fish finder pod that sends sonar images to your handheld device. Fish Pod:  Remotely operated payload release pod that can carry your bait or lure to the inaccessible waterways. Film Pod: waterproof camera that can film in the air as well as under the water's surface. With many more pods in development! The AguaDrone Solutions: Commercial fishing vessels use extensive amounts of fuel to find fish.  AguaDrone can extend the vessels reach by spot checking waters without the cost of fuel and in a fraction of the time. Sport fisherman on shore have always struggled with the ability to locate fish and casting limitations.  AguaDrone can spot check waters, sending sonar images to a handheld device.  Once the fish are found AguaDrone can fly your line to fish. Water and drones typically do not mix well together. With AguaDrone's 100% waterproof hull water is no-longer an issue.  land in and take off from fresh or saltwater. Filming from a drone can now be done from the air or under the water's surface with  our waterproof drone and waterproof camera.

Description: MuChat is a social discovery app aimed at helping you find the friends you haven't met yet.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Every new app is aimed at keeping you connected with your friends, but what about the friends you haven't met yet? MuChat aims to solve this by connecting you with people purely by your mutual interests, but there is a catch.  When you open the app you will be presented with a slick UI that shows you the top 25 tags ranked by interest. Selecting a tag will provide you with matches to other people who also subscribe to those tags. From here you can start the conversation, but much like in real life you will not know what they are interested in until the first message has been sent. Once the conversation is underway a drawer will become available listing all of the things you have in common with them. MuChat aims to be the easiest way to meet new friends. We have an ambitious goal to break down the social barriers of meeting new friends similar to what tinder has done for the dating world. We have just released our first version with many planned improvements coming very shortly. Specifically we will be creating a Trending and Latest tag feed that will provide users with fresh tags to make connections with.  We have silently released our first version to the app store in US/CAN. Look forward to having you join the conversation. https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/muchat
